tests.title: Test Login page with incorrect credentials
tests.fullTitle: DLS - Login Page Test Login page with incorrect credentials
tests.code:
var readerHome = client.page.LoginPage();
readerHome.navigate(client.launch_url);
readerHome.login('qa8','admin1','Compro11');
readerHome.expect.element('@credentialsAlert').text.to.equal('Invalid Credential');
client.end();
